### School Management API Check File (Supporting User Management)
### Base URL: https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
### Used for: School selection (list user's schools), school user management (admin), membership requests.
### These endpoints support the "/schools/current" frontend route and school-based role assignment.

@baseUrl = https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
@schoolId = 200
@userId = 12345
@requestId = 300

@accessToken = 

### 1. List all schools (public? may not require auth)
# GET /schools
# Response: { "items": [ { id, name, picture, priority, ... } ] }
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools

### 2. Get details of a specific school
# GET /schools/{school_id}
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. List users belonging to a school (admin only)
# GET /schools/{school_id}/users
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
# Response: { "items": [ { id, username, first_name, last_name, email, phone, ... } ] }
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Add an existing user to a school (admin)
# POST /schools/{school_id}/users
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
# Request body: username, role_id
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "role_id": 5
}

### 5. Remove a user from a school (admin)
# DELETE /schools/{school_id}/users/{user_id}
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. Request membership to a school (student/teacher)
# POST /schools/{school_id}/requests
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
# Request body: role_id, description (optional)
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role_id": 3,
  "description": "I would like to join as a student"
}

### 7. List membership requests for a school (admin)
# GET /schools/{school_id}/requests
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8. Approve a school membership request (admin)
# POST /schools/{school_id}/requests/{request_id}
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/requests/{{requestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 9. Reject a school membership request (admin)
# DELETE /schools/{school_id}/requests/{request_id}
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/requests/{{requestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}